(41, 10, 41, 59, 4, 5, 5, 'much displeased with James and John', 'Envy and Displeasure Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of envy present in both passages. In Mark 10:41, the displeasure of the ten reflects a competitive spirit, while James 4:5 addresses the spirit that ''lusteth to envy.''', 'theme', 0.307, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 10, 42, 42, 22, 25, 25, 'exercise lordship over them', 'Authority and Leadership Over Gentiles', 'Both passages emphasize the exercise of authority by leaders over the Gentiles. They highlight a similar understanding of leadership dynamics in the context of power and authority.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 10, 42, 60, 5, 3, 3, 'exercise authority upon them', 'Authority and Leadership in Scripture', 'This connection highlights the contrast between worldly authority and spiritual leadership. Both passages emphasize the importance of serving rather than exercising lordship over others.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 10, 42, 40, 20, 25, 25, 'exercise authority upon them', 'Authority of Gentile Rulers', 'Both passages emphasize the exercise of authority by rulers over the Gentiles. They highlight a similar understanding of leadership and dominion in the context of power dynamics.', 'parallel', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 10, 43, 40, 23, 8, 12, 'shall be your minister', 'Servanthood and Humility', 'Both passages emphasize the idea that greatness is defined by servanthood and humility. Mark 10:43 states that the great among you shall be your minister, while Matthew 23:11 reinforces that the greatest shall be your servant.', 'theme', 0.412, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 10, 43, 42, 14, 11, 11, 'whosoever will be great among you', 'Humility and Greatness', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of humility in relation to greatness. Mark 10:43 highlights that true greatness comes from serving others, while Luke 14:11 states that those who humble themselves will be exalted.', 'theme', 0.398, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
